'''Nepal''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in December 2019. Its default city is only the capital, Kathmandu.

In December 2019 on iOS; new countries were added. Along with Nepal; there was also Austria, Bahamas, Costa Rica, DR Congo, Kazakhstan, Kenya, Kuwait, Lebanon, Mongolia, Ukraine, and Vietnam. This was added in the ''Friends'' Update.

